Uses of Interface
com.genesyslab.platform.apptemplate.configuration.IGApplicationConfiguration.IGPortInfo

  • Packages that use IGApplicationConfiguration.IGPortInfo 
    Package Description
    com.genesyslab.platform.apptemplate.configuration
    Provides helper classes that read application options and other data from Configuration Server, converts it to corresponding Platform SDK objects and makes it easier to set up connections to backend servers and other applications.

    • Uses of IGApplicationConfiguration.IGPortInfo in com.genesyslab.platform.apptemplate.configuration

      This class is an extension of base GApplicationConfiguration.GPortInfo structure with logic related to COM AB information extraction as detached configuration data.
